text: The enigmatic moray (Gymnothorax enigmaticus), also known as the tiger moray or banded moray,Gymnothorax enigmaticus at www.fishbase.org. is a moray eel found in coral reefs in the Pacific and Indian oceans.Gymnothorax enigmaticus at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by McCosker and Randall in 1982, ==References== ==External links== * Fishes of Australia : Gymnothorax enigmaticus enigmatic moray Category:Marine fish of Northern Australia enigmatic moray
